// math.flow - Functions that return values

to add a and b:
    return a + b

to multiply a and b:
    return a * b

to square x:
    return x * x

to factorial n:
    if n <= 1:
        return 1
    return n * factorial (n - 1)

to start:
    say "2 + 3 ="
    say add 2 and 3

    say "4 * 5 ="
    say multiply 4 and 5

    say "7 squared ="
    say square 7

    say "5! ="
    say factorial 5
